'''Joe Kivel''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.


==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[Senior Bowl (bridge)|d'Orsi Senior Bowl]] (1) 2001 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

